<h2 id="download">Download</h2>

<h3 id="windows">Windows</h3>

<p><a href="https://os.mbed.com/teams/ST/wiki/ST-Link-Driver">ST Link Driver</a></p>

<p><a href="https://ko.osdn.net/projects/ttssh2/releases/">Trea Term</a></p>

<h2 id="example-code">Example Code</h2>

<pre><code class="language-C++">#include "mbed.h"

// define the Serial object
Serial pc(USBTX, USBRX);

DigitalOut led1(LED1);

int main() {
    while (true) {
        led1 = !led1;

        // Print something over the serial connection
        pc.printf("Blink! LED is now %d\r\n", led1.read());

        wait(0.5);
    }
}
</code></pre>

<h2 id="seeing-the-log-message">Seeing the Log Message</h2>

<h3 id="windows-1">Windows</h3>

<ol>
  <li>open TeraTerm</li>
  <li>File &gt; New connetion</li>
  <li>Serial Button</li>
  <li>Chooce <code class="highlighter-rouge">mbed Serial Port</code></li>
  <li>Click OK</li>
  <li>Log message</li>
</ol>

